      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an affordable price. A practical choice for buyers seeking dependable basic mobility, with honest wear consistent with age and use. If you want inexpensive wheels without overpaying, this is a smart value opportunity.",
