      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts a conversation for anyone wanting basic transport, a project, or a handy runabout without spending a fortune. Priced honestly and presented as-is, it\u2019s a straightforward buy from someone who believes in being upfront. If you\u2019re practical, don\u2019t mind a few rough edges, and want something budget-friendly with potential, this could be well worth a look.",
