      "description": "Strong-running used car with a solid mechanical foundation and plenty of life left in the drivetrain. It shows cosmetic age and needs the usual TLC you\u2019d expect from an older vehicle, but it starts, runs, and drives with the kind of honest road manners that make it a great budget daily, weekend project, or parts-friendly platform. The powertrain feels eager, the chassis is serviceable, and it offers a lot of usable vehicle for the money. If you want an affordable car with good bones and real potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
